cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with modeling visual relations between objects and proposes a novel approach for the same. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a weakly-supervised discriminative clustering model to learn relations from image-level labels only. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper proposes a model that learns visual relations between objects. 
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a possible category as the paper deals with natural language prepositions and verbs that link pairs of objects. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper introduces a new challenging dataset of unusual relations (UnRel) together with an exhaustive annotation, that enables accurate evaluation of visual relation retrieval.
